import React from 'react'
import { Button, Card, CardActions, CardContent, Typography, Grid } from '@material-ui/core'

const MyCard = () => {
    return (
        <Card>
            <CardContent>
                <Grid container justify="center">
                    <Grid item>
                        <Typography>First Team</Typography>
                    </Grid>
                    <Grid item>
                        <Typography>VS</Typography>

                    </Grid>
                    <Grid item>
                        <Typography>Second Team</Typography>

                    </Grid>
                </Grid>
            </CardContent>
            <CardActions>
                <Grid cont>
                    <Button variant="outlined" color="primary">
                        Show Detail
                </Button>
                    <Button variant="outlined" color="primary">
                        {new Date().toString()}
                    </Button>
               </Grid>
            </CardActions>
        </Card>
    )
}
export default MyCard
